<p class="en">
There was a time I would post photos like this almost every day.  But that is in the past.
</p>

   <p class="jp">    
<span class="title_jp">ビーチ・サンセット</span>
夕日がブラフ・コーブの上の崖を黄金色に照らす。
太平洋に沈む夕日、ハーモサ・ビーチの16th St.にて。
